descriptor.short_desc:
- Ready to serve Energy drink. Best served when chilled.

Note: Not recommended for children, pregnant or lactating women and persons sensitive to caffeine

Country of Origin: Austria
descriptor.long_desc:
Red Bull Energy Drink 250ml is a useful beverage that revitalizes the body and mind. It is a top choice of billions of people across the world, including athletes.

- Red Bull cans are made of 100% recyclable aluminium.
- Red Bull produces a variety of energy drinks in both sugar and sugar-free varieties.

About the Brand: Red Bull is an energy drink brand from Austria. In 1987, Red Bull not only launched a completely new product, it created a whole new product category — energy drinks. From day one, Red Bull has been setting many milestones in sports and culture. Red Bull is appreciated worldwide by top athletes, busy professionals, university students and travelers on long journeys.

descriptor.name: Red Bull Energy Drink, The Summer Edition, Apricot-Strawberry, 250 ml
descriptor.long_desc:
Red Bull Summer Edition's special formula contains ingredients of high-quality caffeine, taurine, B-Group vitamins, sugars, and water. One 250ml can of Red Bull Summer Edition contains 75mg of caffeine, about the same amount as in a cup of home-brewed coffee. The amount of sugar in a can of Red Bull Summer Edition is comparable to the level of sugar in an equivalent amount of apple or orange juice which is 11g per 100 ml. The new limited Red Bull Summer Edition comes with the taste of Apricot- Strawberry that vitalizes body and mind.

- An energy drink that is appreciated worldwide by top athletes, students, and in highly demanding professions
- Contains 80 mg of caffeine, about the same amount as in a cup of coffee
- Wheat-free, gluten-free, dairy-free, lactose-free, and vegetarian
- All cans are made of 100% recyclable aluminum

descriptor.name: Novology Sensitive Skin Cleanser, 180 g
descriptor.short_desc:
- Use twice daily

Country of Origin: India
descriptor.long_desc:
Novology Sensitive Skin Cleanser is formulated with potent and active ingredients like Stearic Acid and Palmitic Acid which gently cleanses without irritating the sensitive skin. This cleanser is formulated with palmitic acid also a fatty acid found in the skin and in palm oil and kernel oil. Stearic acid is a long chain fatty acid. It is also a major component of cocoa and shea butter. This 2%Palmitic Acid + Stearic Acid is a gentle and non-foaming cleanser which cleanses without any irritation or redness on the skin. It helps in replenishing the skin barrier and is safe to use for all skin types especially dry, damaged, dehydrated, and irritated skin.
- A non-foaming cleanser that cleanses without any irritation or redness on the skin
- Enriched with 2%Palmitic Acid + Stearic Acid that helps in replenishing the skin barrier
- Safe to use for all skin types especially dry, damaged, dehydrated, and irritated skin
